 VGM Example E02
 Converting geometry from Root to Geant4
 ---------------------------------------
 
 Source: Root geometry file N03Example.root
         Geant4 novice N03 example
         
 1. The provided installation script (E02/install.sh)
    will install Geant4 N03 example  with modifications
    for VGM demostration in E02 directory:
    ./install.sh
    
    This step is not necessary if you installed all examples
    at once from up directory.
  
 
 2. Define environment variables for this example
    (your environment for VGM has to be set first, see doc/INSTALL)
    source env_setup.csh  OR  
    . env_setup.sh
    
 3. Run example, the geometry will be imported during initialization
    cd N03
    exampleN03
